Eau_Claire.Regis High School (Wisconsin): Regis High School is a co-ed Catholic high school in Eau Claire, Wisconsin United States in the Diocese of La Crosse. The school serves grades 9 through 12 in high school, while the school building also houses Regis Middle School which serves grades 6 through 8. It is part of the Regis Catholic Schools system, which also includes three elementary schools.
